Ad [Addendum] 51. Witt Library. 'Assassini' - 'Attack': 1) Liechtenstein, Vienna (Photo); 2) University Gall. Stockholm Old Photo not very good. Looks better than Liechtenstein where sheep added in background from Unfaithful Shepherd; 3) Brunsvik Sale, Vienna, Dorotheum 25-XI-1906, N° 47 (P.B.II), Eichenholz 126 x 97 cm stark übermalt. Rather poor; 4) With different background and two figures on right altered, (Stchavinsky Coll. Petrograd, N° 16. Quite good, later (by ??) see also P.B.II.
